            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">启蒙与启蒙的敌人有着近似的面孔，只是理性成为了上帝，未来替换了彼岸</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="886664136">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-886664136" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-886664136" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="886664136">有用</a>
